    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isn't the \"common-sense\" part just an opinion? like, how can you say they're a solution when a lot of people argue that more guns actually make things more dangerous for self-defense? and what about the legal side—the second amendment is pretty clear about the right to bear arms, isn't it?",
